title: Art of the Pacific (Art Ebook).pdf
description:
Pdf / English / 1980 / 239 pages / 36.7 MB

Much of the fabulous art produced by Maori, Polynesian, and Melanesian peoples has
remained in the South Pacific, where it was created. This book presents for the first time a stunning treasury of masterpieces of this ethnographical art from New Zealand museums, which house the finest and most comprehensive collections of this material in the world.
